high_descs: Pick up the soap next to the sink.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Wet the soap with water in the sink.
Bring the wet soap to the tub.
Put the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the tub.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the bathtub at the end of the room, then turn left to face the kitchen counter
grab the soap off of the kitchen counter
move left a bit to the left side of the sink
rinse the soap out in the sink then pick it back up
move forwards over to the bathtub again
place the soap down inside of the bathtub
anns.task_desc: place rinsed off soap inside of the bathtub

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the bathroom sink
Pick up the pink soap bar right of the sink from the counter
Turn left and walk over to the other side of the counter then face back toward the sink
Rinse the soap under water in the sink and remove it
Turn right and walk over to the bathtub
Put the soap bar in the bathtub
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned soap bar in the bathtub
